brown (see tip). Remove muffins from tin and serve warm or leave to cool completely on a wire rack."}],"hintsAndTricks":["Gluten-free doughs can dry out quite quickly. Keep an eye on the muffins in the oven and remove from oven as soon as they are done."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","55m","12 pieces"]}